rken vor Wien.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 4a17. Jahrhundert. 4aBarockliteratur. 4aDeutsche Literatur. 4aHallmann, Johann Christian. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / German.2bisacsh  aBaroque literature.  aGerman literature.  aSeventeenth century.1 aSeelbach, Ulrich, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2022 Part 1z978311076682008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2022z9783110993738oZDB-23-DKU0 cprintz978311067838340uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311067848240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110678482423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110678482/original  a978-3-11-076682-0  DG Plus DeG Package 2022 Part 1b2022  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2022  aZDB-23-DKUb2022